##If you’re coming to work for a fast growing UK business (‘scale-up’ business)

You may be eligible for a [Scale-up Worker visa](/scale-up-worker-visa) if you’re coming to work in a high-skilled job.

### Eligibility

The eligibility criteria include:

- working in an eligible job, for example a web design consultant or IT business analyst
- having a job offer to work for an approved scale-up business for at least 6 months
+ being paid a minimum salary - how much depends on the type of work you do
- usually proving that you can read, write, speak and understand English

###How long you can stay

Your visa can last for 2 years. You can extend it as long as you’re still eligible.

After 5 years, you may be able to apply to settle permanently in the UK.
